Mexico City. A fatal car crash. Three lives collide.&nbsp;

A teenager risks it all to run away with his brother&rsquo;s wife. A model loses everything after moving in with her lover. A homeless man unearths the ghosts of his past. As their stories unfold, human chaos, cruelty, and tenderness come to light &ndash; revealing they are more connected than they seem.

After 25 years, Alejandro Gonz&aacute;lez I&ntilde;&aacute;rritu&rsquo;s legendary debut returns to the big screen in a stunning restoration.

